  "texts": [
    "The dataset compiles titles and genres of games.",
    "we consider users who engage in gameplay for a duration exceeding 3 hours to have a rating of 5, while others are assigned a rating of 2.",
    "We filter out users and items that interact less than 5 times in the log.",
    "• Amazon-Book [35] refers to a book recommendation dataset, the \"book\" subset of the famous Amazon Product Review dataset 4.",
    "This dataset compiles titles and genres of books from Amazon, collected between 1996 and 2018, with review scores ranging from 1 to 5."
  ]
}